original_title: LEGO Ninjago: Masters of Spinjitzu - Tournament of Elements
overview: When Zane sacrificed himself to stop the Golden Master, the power of the Golden Weapons unlocked new abilities within him, revealing a new layer of titanium. The immense energy dispatch destroyed parts of him and caused Zane to vanish into the Digiverse. Only P.I.X.A.L. was aware of Zane’s digital presence – or so she thought…
title: LEGO Ninjago: Masters of Spinjitzu - Tournament of Elements
